wikipedia_page.main: Elliot James Wilson (born 10 November 1979) is an English cricketer, born in Hertford. He has played three List A games, all in the C&G Trophy: one for Warwickshire Cricket Board in 2002, and two for Lincolnshire in 2003 and 2004. His only wicket at this level was that of Glamorgan's Matthew Maynard in 2004.
